WEBVTT

00:00:00.120 --> 00:00:02.389
Hey, good morning, family. How are y'all

00:00:02.399 --> 00:00:04.710
doing today? Well, as you can see, I'm

00:00:04.720 --> 00:00:06.510
overcoming a little bit, but I feel a lot

00:00:06.520 --> 00:00:09.190
better than I did last night. I did

00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:10.830
the video last night and I had to do it

00:00:10.840 --> 00:00:14.589
over today because it was so bad.

00:00:14.599 --> 00:00:16.470
I told the Lord, "I need to

00:00:16.480 --> 00:00:21.269
redo that."I

00:00:21.269 --> 00:00:21.279
have

00:00:21.279 --> 00:00:23.670
a warning from the Lord to warn you all

00:00:23.680 --> 00:00:25.509
about something that he showed me in the

00:00:25.509 --> 00:00:25.519
spirit—a

00:00:25.519 --> 00:00:29.109
very serious thing. He

00:00:29.119 --> 00:00:30.589
showed me

00:00:30.599 --> 00:00:33.430
about the elections and showed me

00:00:33.440 --> 00:00:36.229
that there were key states of

00:00:36.239 --> 00:00:38.549
corruption that will

00:00:38.559 --> 00:00:40.950
have corruption. He talked to me

00:00:40.960 --> 00:00:43.910
about the House of Representatives,

00:00:43.920 --> 00:00:45.350
the Senate, and

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:47.470
the presidency, but

00:00:47.480 --> 00:00:52.470
he was focused in my prayers about

00:00:52.480 --> 00:00:55.590
the Senate and how important it will

00:00:55.600 --> 00:00:58.150
be for us to win the

00:00:58.160 --> 00:01:00.830
Senate. He showed that we would take the

00:01:00.840 --> 00:01:05.149
House by majority. I'm

00:01:05.159 --> 00:01:06.750
not real educated when it comes to

00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:08.749
politics and stuff, what that means, but

00:01:08.759 --> 00:01:10.429
I'm just telling you the words that he

00:01:10.439 --> 00:01:13.550
used. He said, "You will have the House

00:01:13.560 --> 00:01:16.990
by majority, and you will have the

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:19.550
presidency, but the battle in the

00:01:19.560 --> 00:01:22.950
spirit realm, my son, is the

00:01:22.950 --> 00:01:22.960
Senate."For

00:01:22.960 --> 00:01:28.069
this is a two-seat gap;

00:01:28.079 --> 00:01:30.670
there's a

00:01:30.670 --> 00:01:30.680
two-seat

00:01:30.680 --> 00:01:32.749
victory that you're

00:01:32.759 --> 00:01:36.310
after. There are two seats in limbo,

00:01:36.320 --> 00:01:40.630
basically. He was talking to me

00:01:40.640 --> 00:01:43.709
about Nevada

00:01:43.709 --> 00:01:43.719
and

00:01:43.719 --> 00:01:47.230
Arizona, and he said, "You must pray for

00:01:47.240 --> 00:01:51.270
Ted Cruz."There's

00:01:51.270 --> 00:01:51.280
an attack

00:01:51.280 --> 00:01:54.310
trying to take him out of

00:01:54.320 --> 00:01:57.789
his position, and the Lord said,

00:01:57.799 --> 00:02:01.910
"You must intercede for Ted

00:02:01.910 --> 00:02:01.920
Cruz."Then

00:02:01.920 --> 00:02:03.910
he showed me Pennsylvania.

00:02:03.920 --> 00:02:06.709
I know what I'm saying is more than two

00:02:06.719 --> 00:02:09.350
seats, but I'm just telling you exactly

00:02:09.360 --> 00:02:11.470
what the Lord said. I'm not taking away

00:02:11.480 --> 00:02:14.589
any and I'm not adding to it. So the math

00:02:14.599 --> 00:02:16.830
on it doesn't make sense, but it does

00:02:16.840 --> 00:02:19.390
because it's what he said. He

00:02:19.400 --> 00:02:21.990
said to pray over Texas, for there will

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:24.430
try to be a Blue Wave of

00:02:24.430 --> 00:02:24.440
corruption

00:02:24.440 --> 00:02:28.270
in Texas.

00:02:28.280 --> 00:02:31.150
Not that it would be a Blue

00:02:31.160 --> 00:02:33.470
Wave for them, but it's about Texas, and

00:02:33.480 --> 00:02:34.790
he was talking about something that

00:02:34.800 --> 00:02:36.869
hasn't happened in

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:38.509
a long time or hasn't happened at all. There

00:02:38.509 --> 00:02:38.519
is

00:02:38.519 --> 00:02:40.229
something

00:02:40.239 --> 00:02:42.670
very serious about Texas with Ted Cruz.

00:02:42.680 --> 00:02:45.630
Number two was we have to pray for

00:02:45.640 --> 00:02:48.309
Pennsylvania. The Lord said this is a

00:02:48.319 --> 00:02:50.470
key too; we have to have Pennsylvania.

00:02:50.480 --> 00:02:52.990
Then he said that

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:56.030
these other two states, which were

00:02:56.040 --> 00:02:58.990
Nevada and Arizona, were also in jeopardy.

00:02:59.000 --> 00:03:01.470
I saw blue lines going

00:03:01.480 --> 00:03:03.750
through them and red lines, and it was

00:03:03.760 --> 00:03:05.550
trying to flip either way. That means there

00:03:05.550 --> 00:03:05.560
were

00:03:05.560 --> 00:03:08.350
very close races. The Lord

00:03:08.360 --> 00:03:11.190
said to me, "Brandon, this is very close

00:03:11.200 --> 00:03:15.509
races, very close."There were red lines

00:03:15.519 --> 00:03:17.869
and blue lines, which means it was

00:03:17.879 --> 00:03:20.949
divided. In these states, there were blue

00:03:20.959 --> 00:03:24.550
lines, but in Texas, it was trying to turn

00:03:24.560 --> 00:03:28.350
completely blue. It was a

00:03:28.360 --> 00:03:30.670
bold

00:03:30.680 --> 00:03:32.470
blue, and the Lord said, "You must

00:03:32.480 --> 00:03:36.229
intercede for Ted."Then I saw in the

00:03:36.239 --> 00:03:38.149
spirit Pennsylvania, and it was trying to

00:03:38.159 --> 00:03:42.429
turn blue. It was bold blue, not

00:03:42.439 --> 00:03:45.589
divided, but it was going to try to turn

00:03:45.599 --> 00:03:48.070
blue. The Lord said, "You must pray for

00:03:48.070 --> 00:03:48.080
this."I

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:50.190
don't know why he didn't say

00:03:50.200 --> 00:03:52.149
to pray for any others, but these are the

00:03:52.159 --> 00:03:53.789
ones he said there would be some

00:03:53.799 --> 00:03:55.710
corruptions that you have to come

00:03:55.720 --> 00:04:01.030
against. Then I was shown

00:04:01.040 --> 00:04:06.670
Hispanic women in a room. I

00:04:06.680 --> 00:04:08.990
have to be very careful for the safety of my

00:04:09.000 --> 00:04:13.309
family, but I'll use

00:04:13.309 --> 00:04:13.319
keywords

00:04:13.319 --> 00:04:16.949
with what I was shown. I hope you are

00:04:16.959 --> 00:04:19.590
in tune enough to

00:04:19.600 --> 00:04:21.390
understand what I'm about to say without

00:04:21.400 --> 00:04:23.110
putting this live with hundreds of thousands

00:04:23.120 --> 00:04:25.469
of people.

00:04:25.479 --> 00:04:28.870
I

00:04:28.880 --> 00:04:32.189
heard the word

00:04:32.189 --> 00:04:32.199
"asylum"—promises

00:04:32.199 --> 00:04:34.230
of

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:37.510
asylum for doing a certain

00:04:37.520 --> 00:04:40.430
task. Lots of people that were coming

00:04:40.440 --> 00:04:43.350
over the border were promised a certain

00:04:43.360 --> 00:04:46.350
thing if they were to do something to

00:04:46.360 --> 00:04:50.710
help them. I saw white tables

00:04:50.720 --> 00:04:53.909
and Hispanic women behind these

00:04:53.919 --> 00:04:55.749
tables. You can just think about what

00:04:55.759 --> 00:04:58.710
they're doing. I saw these white

00:04:58.720 --> 00:05:01.270
tables with metal chairs,

00:05:01.280 --> 00:05:04.390
and I saw many Hispanic

00:05:04.400 --> 00:05:06.710
women behind these tables. I saw a

00:05:06.720 --> 00:05:09.070
metal building, like a

00:05:09.080 --> 00:05:11.310
container building, and

00:05:12.759 --> 00:05:14.510
there were pods with people inside

00:05:14.520 --> 00:05:17.590
of them. I was told the word

00:05:17.590 --> 00:05:17.600
"asylum."I'm

00:05:17.600 --> 00:05:20.430
not going to say what

00:05:20.440 --> 00:05:22.870
they were doing, but I will tell you: you

00:05:22.880 --> 00:05:25.870
must pray against corruption.

00:05:25.880 --> 00:05:30.110
Because of

00:05:30.120 --> 00:05:35.469
asylum, I heard,

00:05:35.479 --> 00:05:38.029
"We have to cover the evidence;

00:05:38.039 --> 00:05:40.550
loose lips sink

00:05:40.550 --> 00:05:40.560
ships."The

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:44.070
people

00:05:44.080 --> 00:05:47.150
disappeared;

00:05:47.160 --> 00:05:49.270
they were dealt

00:05:49.280 --> 00:05:57.550
with.

00:05:57.560 --> 00:06:01.749
They were lied to

00:06:01.749 --> 00:06:01.759
and deceived.

00:06:01.759 --> 00:06:04.710
We deal with a very evil

00:06:04.720 --> 00:06:07.350
enemy and a very evil

00:06:07.360 --> 00:06:09.990
government. We deal with people that have

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:13.390
no conscience for life; they don't

00:06:13.400 --> 00:06:17.309
care. People are very

00:06:17.319 --> 00:06:19.749
power-hungry.

00:06:19.759 --> 00:06:22.710
When you see people that are

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:25.350
desperate, desperate people do immoral

00:06:25.350 --> 00:06:25.360
and ungodly

00:06:25.360 --> 00:06:28.189
things.

00:06:28.199 --> 00:06:32.350
We must pray

00:06:32.360 --> 00:06:36.909
for this

00:06:36.919 --> 00:06:39.469
assignment. He said

00:06:39.479 --> 00:06:42.309
the enemy's plan is already

00:06:42.319 --> 00:06:46.150
afoot.

00:06:46.160 --> 00:06:48.390
He said, "Brandon, you

00:06:48.400 --> 00:06:50.950
must pray, for this is a war in the

00:06:50.960 --> 00:06:53.150
spirit realm, a war in the heavenlies."It

00:06:53.150 --> 00:06:53.160
is a

00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:56.629
very serious time, for you must

00:06:56.639 --> 00:06:59.150
have all branches of the government—the

00:06:59.150 --> 00:06:59.160
legislature,

00:06:59.160 --> 00:07:02.589
Senate, House, and

00:07:02.589 --> 00:07:02.599
presidency—for

00:07:02.599 --> 00:07:04.909
what I have planned for

00:07:04.919 --> 00:07:07.350
this nation to turn things around. He

00:07:07.360 --> 00:07:09.950
said it will be delayed if you

00:07:09.960 --> 00:07:12.830
do not.

00:07:12.840 --> 00:07:15.430
There is a battle to be

00:07:15.440 --> 00:07:18.309
won, and you are to bring forth

00:07:18.319 --> 00:07:20.990
prayer because with much prayer and

00:07:21.000 --> 00:07:23.390
intercession, my angels are working

00:07:23.400 --> 00:07:25.869
on

00:07:25.879 --> 00:07:28.430
your behalf. This is a strategic plan

00:07:28.440 --> 00:07:30.589
from the Father. He said, "Call my

00:07:30.599 --> 00:07:34.189
troops together, my body, and call them to

00:07:34.189 --> 00:07:34.199
intercede."In

00:07:34.199 --> 00:07:36.550
your intercession for

00:07:36.560 --> 00:07:39.390
America, you will turn things. He said,

00:07:39.400 --> 00:07:42.589
"As what I position you to do

00:07:42.599 --> 00:07:44.830
on this platform, I am calling you to do

00:07:44.840 --> 00:07:47.029
this much more."It's not just going

00:07:47.039 --> 00:07:49.270
to be for 30 days, for we have much

00:07:49.280 --> 00:07:52.149
work to do.

00:07:52.159 --> 00:07:54.309
He said, "You will pray continually even

00:07:54.319 --> 00:07:56.710
after the 30 days until I release you

00:07:56.720 --> 00:07:59.550
from this."I thought it was

00:07:59.560 --> 00:08:02.909
a 30-day assignment, but the

00:08:02.909 --> 00:08:02.919
Commander-in-Chief

00:08:02.919 --> 00:08:04.909
of all things, my

00:08:04.919 --> 00:08:07.270
Lord and Savior Jesus Christ, has told me

00:08:07.280 --> 00:08:09.950
that my job is to pray with you for

00:08:09.950 --> 00:08:09.960
an

00:08:09.960 --> 00:08:11.909
extended period of time.

00:08:11.909 --> 00:08:11.919
I'll

00:08:11.919 --> 00:08:14.869
do my best to do it

00:08:14.879 --> 00:08:16.990
every single day.

00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:18.629
I'm telling you

00:08:18.639 --> 00:08:20.110
that it will be as much as I

00:08:20.110 --> 00:08:20.120
can

00:08:20.120 --> 00:08:23.869
possibly handle. There

00:08:23.869 --> 00:08:23.879
is

00:08:23.879 --> 00:08:28.189
a very stern warning

00:08:28.189 --> 00:08:28.199
and

00:08:28.199 --> 00:08:31.189
an urgency. It

00:08:31.199 --> 00:08:34.029
is not time to "play church"anymore. It is

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:37.909
time to come up higher with the fire. If

00:08:37.919 --> 00:08:39.110
you're going to church just to get a

00:08:39.110 --> 00:08:39.120
seeker-friendly

00:08:39.120 --> 00:08:40.949
message

00:08:40.959 --> 00:08:43.670
and you're not getting fed,

00:08:43.680 --> 00:08:45.190
you need to find a church that will

00:08:45.200 --> 00:08:47.150
teach you the word of God and teach you

00:08:47.160 --> 00:08:49.670
how to be strong. Many of you

00:08:49.680 --> 00:08:51.550
tell me, "Brother Brandon, I'm not

00:08:51.560 --> 00:08:53.990
getting fed where I'm at."Then I

00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:56.630
would say shop around by the

00:08:56.640 --> 00:08:58.509
Holy Spirit.

00:09:04.800 --> 00:09:07.389
It is not a time

00:09:07.399 --> 00:09:10.790
to be lukewarm and

00:09:10.800 --> 00:09:13.310
shy away from being bold about what

00:09:13.320 --> 00:09:16.350
God has us to do. We have got to become

00:09:16.360 --> 00:09:19.230
stronger in our faith and be on fire.

00:09:19.240 --> 00:09:21.670
When I went to these meetings, I became

00:09:21.680 --> 00:09:24.389
spoiled. When you are underneath

00:09:24.399 --> 00:09:26.470
the glory like I was, we felt the

00:09:26.480 --> 00:09:27.750
presence of the Lord. You're

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:29.750
hungry; it stirs you up to the

00:09:29.760 --> 00:09:31.990
point that you want more.

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:34.710
To me, there's nothing more in

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:37.389
this world that I want—not fame, not

00:09:37.399 --> 00:09:40.509
money, not popularity.

00:09:43.600 --> 00:09:47.389
I want Jesus.

00:09:47.399 --> 00:09:49.790
Whenever I have a

00:09:49.800 --> 00:09:51.550
visitation like I've had the last couple

00:09:51.560 --> 00:09:53.430
weeks from Nancy Dufresne having healing

00:09:53.440 --> 00:09:55.750
ministries, Billy Burke,

00:09:55.750 --> 00:09:55.760
Billye

00:09:55.760 --> 00:09:57.150
Brim, and all the things that we've been

00:09:57.160 --> 00:09:58.910
under, you talk

00:09:58.920 --> 00:10:01.870
about your flame. If you're in a place

00:10:01.880 --> 00:10:05.230
of drought spiritually, all you have to

00:10:05.240 --> 00:10:07.509
do is step in the river. God didn't make

00:10:07.519 --> 00:10:09.069
it hard for us to

00:10:09.079 --> 00:10:10.829
get on fire for him.

00:10:12.680 --> 00:10:14.509
But you can't just sit on your

00:10:14.519 --> 00:10:16.910
couch and watch Friends

00:10:16.920 --> 00:10:18.509
and go, "Well, I'm going to grow up

00:10:18.519 --> 00:10:21.470
and do something

00:10:21.470 --> 00:10:21.480
eventually."You've

00:10:21.480 --> 00:10:24.030
got to put yourself in a position of

00:10:24.040 --> 00:10:26.710
feeding yourself spiritually and fanning

00:10:26.720 --> 00:10:29.310
that flame on a continual basis. I refuse

00:10:29.320 --> 00:10:31.829
to go back to where I was even

00:10:31.839 --> 00:10:33.949
two or three weeks ago. Diana and I

00:10:33.959 --> 00:10:36.790
both said this: we are done with

00:10:36.800 --> 00:10:38.870
those days. We are ready and pressing on.

00:10:38.880 --> 00:10:40.430
I'm going to do

00:10:40.440 --> 00:10:42.190
whatever it takes. If I have to travel

00:10:42.200 --> 00:10:44.509
across the country to find the meetings

00:10:44.519 --> 00:10:47.470
to fan my flame, I will. How desperate, how hungry

00:10:47.480 --> 00:10:51.190
are you?

00:11:04.399 --> 00:11:07.269
I want

00:11:07.279 --> 00:11:10.790
to be an inferno for Jesus. I want

00:11:10.790 --> 00:11:10.800
to be

00:11:10.800 --> 00:11:13.269
filled with and controlled by

00:11:13.279 --> 00:11:15.629
the Holy Ghost, to see a move of

00:11:15.639 --> 00:11:18.670
God in the service where we see signs

00:11:18.680 --> 00:11:20.550
and wonders that follow them that

00:11:20.550 --> 00:11:20.560
believe—people

00:11:20.560 --> 00:11:23.069
getting saved and

00:11:23.079 --> 00:11:25.670
baptized in the Holy Ghost and fire.

00:11:28.120 --> 00:11:31.069
My job is to tell

00:11:31.079 --> 00:11:34.110
you Jesus Christ is coming. My job is to

00:11:34.120 --> 00:11:36.269
warn you that the Father is coming and

00:11:36.269 --> 00:11:36.279
to

00:11:36.279 --> 00:11:38.629
lead salvation. If you

00:11:38.639 --> 00:11:40.990
don't know Jesus Christ as your Lord and

00:11:41.000 --> 00:11:43.350
Savior, you're going to go to hell.

00:11:48.920 --> 00:11:51.430
Jesus is

00:11:59.000 --> 00:12:01.870
wonderful. It's time to come up

00:12:01.880 --> 00:12:04.629
higher, stopping our stupid

00:12:04.639 --> 00:12:09.230
little theology differences

00:12:09.230 --> 00:12:09.240
and

00:12:09.240 --> 00:12:12.590
coming up higher with the fire so that we

00:12:12.600 --> 00:12:15.550
are one as the body of Christ.

00:12:15.560 --> 00:12:17.710
We may not agree on everything,

00:12:24.600 --> 00:12:26.990
but as long as

00:12:27.000 --> 00:12:28.590
we're trying for the same thing and

00:12:30.720 --> 00:12:32.870
our mission is to

00:12:32.880 --> 00:12:36.269
get people saved and

00:12:36.279 --> 00:12:38.030
baptized in the Holy Ghost,

00:12:40.199 --> 00:12:42.189
teaching them how to become stronger in

00:12:42.199 --> 00:12:43.990
the Lord,

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:45.509
that's what the whole mission should be.

00:12:45.519 --> 00:12:47.629
We don't have

00:12:47.639 --> 00:12:49.790
to agree on tithing.

00:12:54.480 --> 00:12:56.590
I believe in giving

00:12:56.600 --> 00:12:58.550
the way I give,

00:12:58.560 --> 00:13:00.030
and there's

00:13:00.040 --> 00:13:01.710
fruit behind what I say.

00:13:03.519 --> 00:13:05.189
I'm

00:13:05.199 --> 00:13:07.150
blessed, and the Lord has blessed me.

00:13:09.000 --> 00:13:10.629
What I do is working, so I'm going to

00:13:10.639 --> 00:13:12.829
keep doing it.

00:13:26.279 --> 00:13:29.269
God is a faithful God.

00:13:32.110 --> 00:13:32.120
It's

00:13:34.480 --> 00:13:37.150
taken

00:13:39.639 --> 00:13:42.069
years

00:13:42.079 --> 00:13:43.910
of

00:13:43.920 --> 00:13:46.509
sowing

00:13:46.519 --> 00:13:50.069
and

00:13:50.079 --> 00:13:52.590
giving into right

00:13:52.600 --> 00:13:55.629
soil. The Bible says there

00:13:55.629 --> 00:13:55.639
is

00:13:55.639 --> 00:13:58.350
some 30, some 60,

00:13:58.360 --> 00:14:00.829
and some 100-fold ground. You have to

